{"tid":1536593,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[核彈]我地仲有公眾知情權迫狗鐵公開831 CCTV!!!","createTime":"2019-09-03T16:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T10:51:18.000Z","uid":89254,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"47cb3846066beab5b20e434a067d2c57c9c3e62d","tid":1536593,"uid":89254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:34:57.000Z","msg":"相信大家對831嘅事都感到人神共憤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家我地要迫黨鐵公開831 CCTV先有可能還原到831有冇死到人嘅真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拿我話你知，我地其實一直以黎都忘記咗一樣好重要嘅公民權利，就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公眾知情權</span></span>，呢個權利分分鐘可以嚇撚到黨鐵公開有關片段<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街黨鐵話唔公開831 CCTV理由係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">「涉及大量乘客臉貌」</span><br />\n</span>，但你地記唔記得721元朗恐怖襲擊係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有公開片段</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁即係代表乜野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就係當公眾利益遠大於個人/私人利益時，政府、公營/私營機構應主動披露相關資料。既然721都公開到，點解831唔可以先？我地就要捉住呢點同黨鐵玩到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更何況狗狗們都曾經玩過呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />8月6 condom仔就係用公眾知情權做<span style=\"color: red;\">免死金牌</span>公然違反檢控程序去示範鐳射槍威力做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知你地懶search埋俾你地，<br />\n《公開資料守則》: <a href=\"https://www.access.gov.hk/filemanager/content/codeonacctoinfo/guidelines_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.access.gov.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Fcontent%2Fcodeonacctoinfo%2Fguidelines_c.pdf&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6viVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=2dce8e0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.access.gov.hk/filemanager/content/codeonacctoinfo/guidelines_c.pdf</a><br />\n831地鐵事件明顯無底觸其第二部「可拒絕披露的資料」。同時間警方於831拒絕記者採訪亦都明顯<span style=\"color: green;\">抵觸咗公眾知情權</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我地要做啲咩？就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煲大831!</span></span> 唔理你係日日去太子站跪又好圍警署又好瘋狂文宣又好，我地要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">化公眾知情權做核彈級嘅武器！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，都要廣召相關法律界人士幫手，同我推到上熱門！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nReference:<br />\n<br />\n港鐵劉天成：不宜公開CCTV<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/370703/逃犯條例-警入太子站行動惹爭議-港鐵劉天成-不宜公開cctv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F370703%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%AD%A6%E5%85%A5%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E6%83%B9%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%8A%89%E5%A4%A9%E6%88%90-%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8Bcctv&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6viVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=18373055\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/370703/逃犯條例-警入太子站行動惹爭議-港鐵劉天成-不宜公開cctv</a><br />\n<br />\n示範鐳射槍 vs 公眾知情權:<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2421239/【反修例】被指示範鐳射槍威力違檢控程序%E3%80%80警：衡量公眾知情權不需要問律政司\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2421239%2F%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E7%A4%BA%E7%AF%84%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E6%A7%8D%E5%A8%81%E5%8A%9B%E9%81%95%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%25E3%2580%2580%E8%AD%A6%EF%BC%9A%E8%A1%A1%E9%87%8F%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E7%9F%A5%E6%83%85%E6%AC%8A%E4%B8%8D%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%95%8F%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6viVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=87b951b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2421239/【反修例】被指示範鐳射槍威力違檢控程序%E3%80%80警：衡量公眾知情權不需要問律政司</a><br />\n<br />\n個人資料 (私隱) 條例 網站：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcpd.org.hk/tc_chi/data_privacy_law/code_of_practices/code.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcpd.org.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fdata_privacy_law%2Fcode_of_practices%2Fcode.html&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6viVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=aec65a7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcpd.org.hk/tc_chi/data_privacy_law/code_of_practices/code.html</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap486!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap486%21zh-Hant-HK&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6viVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=b856ea35\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap486!zh-Hant-HK</a>"},{"pid":"c3ae59e6f4977cf358a88235d488546ececb7390","tid":1536593,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad6bfb75f7aa1e3b08b1d636c3bf11fd2cc8589","tid":1536593,"uid":89254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:35:41.000Z","msg":"自推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3f2695fa4133423e3e7df78c908a318bbff771","tid":1536593,"uid":89254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:35:56.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"7c05cf6d137f8349daedcd590bb8822ec940925f","tid":1536593,"uid":89254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim