ry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n追究到底！"},{"pid":"32360177ff62c2e8f835b0b8c87d953f4db3491e","tid":1536593,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:27:58.000Z","msg":"要搵法律撚幫拖 投訴狗鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb93e86011f6cff3cf38e9bbfc5663eb44b5b69","tid":1536593,"uid":288389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:49:02.000Z","msg":"毋忘太子死亡事件"},{"pid":"c35dd08b670f14e24040d8a722206ad09fa7d325","tid":1536593,"uid":288389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:53:25.000Z","msg":"推到頂"},{"pid":"26715d56891d559d3872d8c23cf8fe828afeedb6","tid":1536593,"uid":43251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"咩都唔識 淨係識推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b250c8de1c9be908c972e2f2a41d4137ca881b23","tid":1536593,"uid":18695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb73f153f3a897ffa53544aebb87c5f2fa22027","tid":1536593,"uid":89254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e967f1db9056cfe1bd08284309df8c2e58d54d","tid":1536593,"uid":294410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"p 牌推唔到都有推！"},{"pid":"a166c609b03ad7869ba6acdd695320760893caa7","tid":1536593,"uid":242737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:35:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"396faa1bba961843bcde9dc4dfaadce3bcebe922","tid":1536593,"uid":267398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:54:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e1a54